textAfterTable: File Format Description File created by Adobe Proto, an Adobe Touch App used for creating interactive wireframes and website prototypes; can store multiple page layouts, each with interactive elements; supports CSS, WebKit, and jQuery technologies. Adobe Proto designs can be rendered and viewed within standard Web browsers. Saved projects can be uploaded to the Adobe Creative Cloud and then downloaded in Dreamweaver for more extensive editing. NOTE: Adobe Proto has been discontinued and is no longer available for purchase. Program(s) that open .PRO files Windows Adobe Dreamweaver CC Mac OS Adobe Dreamweaver CC iOS Adobe Proto Android
